  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 37-15-30, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO REQUIRE THE USE OF AUTOMOBILE REGISTRATIONS AS PROOF OF RESIDENCY WHEN ENROLLING STUDENTS IN SCHOOL; TO REQUIRE PARENTS OR LEGAL GUARDIANS WHO DO NOT OWN A VEHICLE TO SUBMIT A SIGNED AFFIDAVIT, ATTESTING THAT NO MOTOR VEHICLE IS OWNED AND AFFIRMING THE STUDENT'S ACTUAL RESIDENCE AT THE STATED ADDRESS WITHIN THE ENROLLING SCHOOL DISTRICT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
